Optimal Prime remained cool, he wasn't scared by the fact that he was out 
numbered. "Bring it on boys, I have quite a few surprises of my own," 
Optimal Prime told them. He reached into his subspace compartmeant and 
pulled out some type of black tube. The black tube then extended to be as 
big as Optimal Prime himself, it was some type of telescoping bazooka.
